1
00:00:59,440 --> 00:01:00,320
Boss Yun comes every Wednesday night

2
00:01:00,320 --> 00:01:01,920
to teach the female workers.

3
00:01:02,320 --> 00:01:04,319
She teaches them arithmetic and literacy,

4
00:01:04,319 --> 00:01:06,040
so if their wages get docked,

5
00:01:06,240 --> 00:01:08,640
they won't be clueless about the accounts.

6
00:01:10,240 --> 00:01:11,680
Have you seen this photo?

7
00:01:12,320 --> 00:01:14,520
Did Boss Yun leave from here that night?

8
00:01:16,600 --> 00:01:18,000
Halfway through the class that day,

9
00:01:18,000 --> 00:01:19,960
Boss Yun felt sick and left early.

10
00:01:20,440 --> 00:01:21,720
I was the one who escorted her.

11
00:01:21,720 --> 00:01:23,120
So where did you take her?

12
00:01:23,480 --> 00:01:25,320
Boss Yun passed out on the way.

13
00:01:29,520 --> 00:01:31,650
We should probably go to the hospital.

14
00:01:32,120 --> 00:01:34,000
My place is just around the corner on the right.

15
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:36,200
Let Boss Yun rest at my place for a while.

16
00:01:36,600 --> 00:01:37,440
You mean,

17
00:01:37,960 --> 00:01:40,200
Xiaotangchun was the one who walked her back?

18
00:01:40,200 --> 00:01:40,720
Yes.

19
00:01:41,200 --> 00:01:42,800
Every time Boss Yun went to a private performance,

20
00:01:42,800 --> 00:01:44,400
the troupe would send someone to accompany her.

21
00:01:44,400 --> 00:01:46,479
Boss Yun would make him wait at the alley entrance.

22
00:01:46,479 --> 00:01:48,340
That day, she was the one who came.

23
00:01:50,200 --> 00:01:51,000
Sir,

24
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:52,680
please take a look at this suicide note.

25
00:01:52,680 --> 00:01:53,960
Did Boss Yun write it?

26
00:01:57,479 --> 00:01:58,160
Zhongrong,

27
00:01:58,160 --> 00:01:59,039
the tonal pattern of this death poem

28
00:01:59,039 --> 00:02:00,000
is off.

29
00:02:00,080 --> 00:02:01,520
Boss Yun had more than once

30
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:02,800
criticized such doggerel.

31
00:02:02,800 --> 00:02:04,460
There is no way she wrote this.

32
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:14,130
Did you know Boss Yun is a woman?

33
00:02:15,600 --> 00:02:17,320
Whether the Master is a man or a woman,

34
00:02:17,320 --> 00:02:18,920
it makes no difference to us.

35
00:02:18,920 --> 00:02:20,440
Men and women are equal.

36
00:02:23,880 --> 00:02:24,880
This is for you.

37
00:02:25,640 --> 00:02:28,640
Binding with cloth strips for too long isn't healthy.

38
00:02:32,840 --> 00:02:33,640
Thank you.

39
00:02:36,920 --> 00:02:37,640
You two.

40
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:41,000
I know you are police officers.

41
00:02:41,000 --> 00:02:42,800
Boss Yun definitely wouldn't commit suicide.

42
00:02:42,800 --> 00:02:44,120
Please clear her name.

43
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:50,400
Maybe Xiaotangchun

44
00:02:50,480 --> 00:02:52,200
drugged Boss Yun first,

45
00:02:52,720 --> 00:02:55,240
dressed her in women's clothes at her home,

46
00:02:55,600 --> 00:02:58,200
and dragged her to the street to be exposed.

47
00:02:59,480 --> 00:03:00,520
That suicide note

48
00:03:00,520 --> 00:03:02,180
was likely forged by her, too.

49
00:03:03,120 --> 00:03:05,360
But the old opera house foreman said

50
00:03:05,480 --> 00:03:07,740
she saw Boss Yun buried with her own eyes.

51
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:09,720
Later, someone said they saw Boss Yun.

52
00:03:09,720 --> 00:03:10,780
What's that about?

53
00:03:12,320 --> 00:03:14,380
Feudal ethics really do harm people.

54
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:16,120
If not for the fact

55
00:03:16,200 --> 00:03:17,720
that women couldn't perform back then,

56
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:20,640
why would Boss Yun have needed to disguise herself as a man?

57
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:21,760
What a pity.

58
00:03:24,320 --> 00:03:25,120
Comfortable.

59
00:03:29,360 --> 00:03:30,440
Why keep it?

60
00:03:30,760 --> 00:03:33,020
It should have been thrown away long ago.

61
00:03:58,280 --> 00:03:59,240
Yun...

62
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:00,960
Boss Yun.

63
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:02,880
The road to the underworld is dark.

64
00:04:02,880 --> 00:04:05,280
I want to borrow your flash to light the way.

65
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:07,440
Boss Yun.

66
00:04:07,440 --> 00:04:08,200
I was wrong.

67
00:04:08,360 --> 00:04:09,800
I was wrong.

68
00:04:10,360 --> 00:04:12,360
You said I was a fraud seeking fame.

69
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:13,760
Then tell me,

70
00:04:14,200 --> 00:04:15,480
who did I deceive?

71
00:04:15,720 --> 00:04:16,800
And whose reputation did I steal?

72
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:19,240
I didn't say that.

73
00:04:19,360 --> 00:04:20,880
It was... It was Xiaotangchun who said it.

74
00:04:20,880 --> 00:04:21,720
She said

75
00:04:22,800 --> 00:04:24,240
she was jealous of your reputation.

76
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:25,880
Only if your true identity was revealed,

77
00:04:25,880 --> 00:04:27,600
could she take your place.

78
00:04:28,040 --> 00:04:29,240
She paid me

79
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:30,320
to play along.

80
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:31,600
Money.

81
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:32,720
Money.

82
00:04:36,240 --> 00:04:37,200
It's... it's here.

83
00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:38,000
It's all here.

84
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:40,040
I haven't spent any of this money.

85
00:04:40,040 --> 00:04:42,000
I was saving it to buy incense

86
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:43,240
as an offering to you.

87
00:04:44,520 --> 00:04:45,040
Speak.

88
00:04:45,480 --> 00:04:46,920
How did you work together?

89
00:04:46,920 --> 00:04:49,159
Tell me every single detail.

90
00:04:55,320 --> 00:04:56,480
You aren't Boss Yun.

91
00:05:00,040 --> 00:05:01,560
Spare me.

92
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:02,360
I'll talk.

93
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:04,380
I'll tell you everything.

94
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:06,640
That day,

95
00:05:07,200 --> 00:05:08,120
we agreed

96
00:05:08,240 --> 00:05:09,840
to meet at her house at night.

97
00:05:10,120 --> 00:05:10,640
But

98
00:05:10,680 --> 00:05:12,080
by the time I rushed over,

99
00:05:12,320 --> 00:05:12,960
Boss Yun

100
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:15,800
had already been drugged by Xiaotangchun.

101
00:05:22,160 --> 00:05:23,490
Look at the state of you.

102
00:05:23,840 --> 00:05:24,720
You won't die.

103
00:05:42,440 --> 00:05:43,840
There is no turning back.

104
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:45,680
Have you really thought this through?

105
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:46,409
If we do this,

106
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:49,120
Boss Yun will be completely ruined.

107
00:05:54,440 --> 00:05:55,970
I never understood before,

108
00:05:57,120 --> 00:05:58,520
what it was that I lacked.

109
00:05:59,320 --> 00:06:01,000
Then suddenly, I understood.

110
00:06:02,480 --> 00:06:04,340
It's not that I'm not good enough.

111
00:06:05,400 --> 00:06:07,460
It's just that as long as you are here,

112
00:06:08,440 --> 00:06:09,720
I can never be the star.

113
00:06:11,400 --> 00:06:13,800
You'll be found out sooner or later anyway.

114
00:06:14,840 --> 00:06:16,640
Why not give the troupe to me?

115
00:06:23,960 --> 00:06:25,760
Why does that look like Boss Yun?

116
00:06:26,160 --> 00:06:27,440
Is that Boss Yun?

117
00:06:28,080 --> 00:06:29,360
Why is Boss Yun a woman?

118
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:30,720
Liar!

119
00:06:31,400 --> 00:06:32,360
She's deceiving us!

120
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:32,880
Yeah.

121
00:06:33,200 --> 00:06:33,720
Liar!

122
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:34,580
She tricked us!

123
00:06:35,159 --> 00:06:36,000
How can she be a woman?

124
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:36,680
Exactly.

125
00:06:37,480 --> 00:06:38,040
Right.

126
00:06:38,240 --> 00:06:39,640
She fooled us for so long.

127
00:06:39,880 --> 00:06:41,210
She's just scamming us.

128
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:45,520
So Xiaotangchun killed Boss Yun, right?

129
00:06:46,320 --> 00:06:47,240
I don't know.

130
00:06:47,440 --> 00:06:48,640
I really don't know.

131
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:50,700
We never saw each other again.

132
00:06:50,960 --> 00:06:51,560
But...

133
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:52,200
I heard

134
00:06:52,360 --> 00:06:53,600
Boss Yun's vengeful spirit

135
00:06:53,600 --> 00:06:54,640
kept haunting her.

136
00:06:54,640 --> 00:06:55,240
Later,

137
00:06:55,480 --> 00:06:57,080
it scared her out of her mind.

138
00:06:57,200 --> 00:06:57,800
Maybe,

139
00:06:58,640 --> 00:07:00,240
if I hadn't taken that photo,

140
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:02,000
Boss Yun

141
00:07:02,280 --> 00:07:04,210
wouldn't have committed suicide.

142
00:07:04,320 --> 00:07:05,160
Ever since that day,

143
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:06,720
my hand hasn't stopped shaking.

144
00:07:06,720 --> 00:07:07,560
I... I...

145
00:07:07,880 --> 00:07:09,600
I never took another photo.

146
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:13,580
When Boss Yun protected the famine orphans,

147
00:07:13,680 --> 00:07:15,540
you photographed her good deeds.

148
00:07:15,560 --> 00:07:17,080
But when she was drugged and stripped,

149
00:07:17,080 --> 00:07:18,810
you captured her humiliation.

150
00:07:21,600 --> 00:07:23,130
I was confused for a moment.

151
00:07:23,520 --> 00:07:25,380
I was just trying to make a living.

152
00:07:25,960 --> 00:07:26,400
Come on.

153
00:07:26,400 --> 00:07:27,600
Smile for the camera.

154
00:07:29,320 --> 00:07:30,880
Put this in the papers tomorrow.

155
00:07:30,880 --> 00:07:32,080
The headline will be:

156
00:07:32,480 --> 00:07:34,480
"Unethical Reporter Takes Bribes,

157
00:07:34,800 --> 00:07:35,960
Colludes with Xiaotangchun

158
00:07:35,960 --> 00:07:37,290
to Fabricate Scandal."

159
00:07:38,440 --> 00:07:39,240
Take him away.

160
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:47,440
Tell me,

161
00:07:47,640 --> 00:07:49,120
is it possible...

162
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:51,280
Boss Yun isn't dead at all.

163
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:54,159
It was Yun Feiyan that Xiaotangchun saw that day.

164
00:07:54,159 --> 00:07:55,640
Yun Feiyan sought revenge,

165
00:07:55,640 --> 00:07:57,840
so he killed Xiaotangchun and Meng San.

166
00:08:01,200 --> 00:08:02,880
Even if Boss Yun is really dead,

167
00:08:02,880 --> 00:08:05,080
it definitely wasn't a simple suicide.

168
00:08:10,520 --> 00:08:12,580
Looks like we'll have to ask Boss Yun.

169
00:08:15,440 --> 00:08:16,280
Inspector Lin,

170
00:08:16,280 --> 00:08:17,920
show some respect for the dead.

171
00:08:17,920 --> 00:08:19,800
Boss Yun loved peace and quiet in life.

172
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:21,040
Opening the coffin so rashly

173
00:08:21,040 --> 00:08:22,970
might disturb the soul of the dead.

174
00:08:24,960 --> 00:08:26,960
Disturbing Boss Yun's peace briefly

175
00:08:26,960 --> 00:08:28,420
to clear her name forever.

176
00:08:29,000 --> 00:08:31,530
Someone wants the truth buried with Boss Yun,

177
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:34,210
so we must open the coffin to examine the body.

178
00:08:35,919 --> 00:08:37,679
Today, regarding the case of Yun Feiyan,

179
00:08:37,679 --> 00:08:39,000
the truth remains unclear,

180
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:40,280
and the injustice unredressed.

181
00:08:40,280 --> 00:08:41,720
By law, we conduct this examination.

182
00:08:41,720 --> 00:08:43,360
I humbly pray for your oversight.

183
00:08:43,360 --> 00:08:44,690
Disturbing your spirit

184
00:08:44,760 --> 00:08:46,020
is truly a last resort.

185
00:08:46,360 --> 00:08:46,880
I pray,

186
00:08:47,000 --> 00:08:48,260
for your forgiveness.

187
00:09:33,440 --> 00:09:35,040
This coffin has been opened.

188
00:09:56,600 --> 00:09:58,460
These are fingernail scratches.

189
00:10:01,840 --> 00:10:03,040
Boss Yun wasn't dead.

190
00:10:05,400 --> 00:10:07,560
So, Boss Yun was buried,

191
00:10:07,560 --> 00:10:09,200
woke up again,

192
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:11,320
and escaped the coffin herself.

193
00:10:11,480 --> 00:10:12,600
That explains it.

194
00:10:12,960 --> 00:10:15,080
Xiao Tangchun saw the real Boss Yun.

195
00:10:15,080 --> 00:10:17,040
He went mad from a guilty conscience.

196
00:10:17,040 --> 00:10:17,800
Later,

197
00:10:17,840 --> 00:10:20,370
Yun Feiyan killed Meng San and Xiao Tangchun.

198
00:10:20,560 --> 00:10:22,800
If the killer really is Yun Feiyan,

199
00:10:23,040 --> 00:10:25,320
why didn't she leave the scene after the murders,

200
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:27,120
but instead hide behind the back wall singing

201
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:28,650
until the beggar appeared?

202
00:10:30,880 --> 00:10:32,160
Is it possible

203
00:10:32,240 --> 00:10:34,500
that she wanted to use the singing voice?

204
00:10:34,920 --> 00:10:36,640
Faking the time of death.

205
00:10:37,520 --> 00:10:38,840
Faking the time of death

206
00:10:38,840 --> 00:10:41,440
is usually to provide the killer with an alibi.

207
00:10:42,000 --> 00:10:44,120
But you almost caught her red-handed,

208
00:10:44,120 --> 00:10:45,680
so she failed to establish an alibi.

209
00:10:45,680 --> 00:10:47,410
There might be another killer.

210
00:10:48,200 --> 00:10:49,160
She did this

211
00:10:49,360 --> 00:10:51,560
to give that person an alibi.

212
00:10:51,920 --> 00:10:53,560
Risking getting caught.

213
00:10:54,640 --> 00:10:56,800
Then her relationship with this person

214
00:10:56,800 --> 00:10:58,330
must be something special.

215
00:10:58,600 --> 00:10:59,840
The two victims

216
00:10:59,840 --> 00:11:01,770
were killed by different weapons.

217
00:11:01,920 --> 00:11:03,840
If there were two killers,

218
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:04,970
it would make sense.

219
00:11:06,600 --> 00:11:09,130
You lot are really out of control, aren't you?

220
00:11:09,440 --> 00:11:11,720
Major newspapers are cracking down on fake news.

221
00:11:11,720 --> 00:11:12,880
It's a total mess.

222
00:11:13,200 --> 00:11:15,640
You really think you're some heroes of justice?

223
00:11:15,640 --> 00:11:17,440
It's our duty to uphold justice.

224
00:11:17,720 --> 00:11:18,720
Inspector Zhang.

225
00:11:19,400 --> 00:11:21,000
We pooled our money for the newspaper ad.

226
00:11:21,000 --> 00:11:22,400
Do you think you could...

227
00:11:24,080 --> 00:11:25,940
You want a reimbursement, right?

228
00:11:26,800 --> 00:11:27,720
No problem.

229
00:11:27,920 --> 00:11:30,520
I'll include your severance pay along with it.

230
00:11:36,320 --> 00:11:36,880
Uncle.

231
00:11:37,440 --> 00:11:39,120
We currently believe these two cases...

232
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:40,880
All of Shanghai knows she committed suicide.

233
00:11:40,880 --> 00:11:42,760
You just won't let it rest.

234
00:11:43,920 --> 00:11:44,760
And Lin Lan,

235
00:11:44,960 --> 00:11:46,880
if you stir up trouble again,

236
00:11:46,880 --> 00:11:48,880
pack your bags and go back to France.

237
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:55,200
If the case isn't closed tomorrow,

238
00:11:55,200 --> 00:11:58,880
the Fourth Criminal Investigation Section will be disbanded immediately.

239
00:11:58,880 --> 00:11:59,760
What are you looking at?

240
00:11:59,760 --> 00:12:00,840
Back to work.

241
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:05,690
I never thought our heroic feat yesterday

242
00:12:06,400 --> 00:12:07,920
would go down in history.

243
00:12:11,080 --> 00:12:12,540
Who exactly is that person

244
00:12:13,080 --> 00:12:14,740
that makes it worth it for her?

245
00:12:16,000 --> 00:12:16,840
To your left.

246
00:12:17,160 --> 00:12:18,680
First row, second stack.

247
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:20,960
On the shelf.

248
00:12:21,560 --> 00:12:22,360
Left side.

249
00:12:23,000 --> 00:12:24,520
Second row, second stack.

250
00:12:29,080 --> 00:12:30,040
That's it.

251
00:12:30,360 --> 00:12:33,200
That's all the news about Boss Yun.

252
00:12:37,120 --> 00:12:39,250
There's stuff from so many years here.

253
00:12:39,280 --> 00:12:40,160
Sanxi,

254
00:12:40,360 --> 00:12:42,400
how do you remember where everything is?

255
00:12:42,400 --> 00:12:44,840
As long as Qiao Sanxi has seen it,

256
00:12:45,000 --> 00:12:46,460
she remembers it forever.

257
00:12:47,520 --> 00:12:48,400
I'm also

258
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:50,520
a fan of Boss Yun.

259
00:12:51,600 --> 00:12:53,600
I've read these over and over again.

260
00:12:56,640 --> 00:12:57,720
It must be

261
00:12:57,720 --> 00:12:59,920
someone close to her.

262
00:13:00,120 --> 00:13:01,000
I checked.

263
00:13:01,000 --> 00:13:02,120
She only had a father,

264
00:13:02,120 --> 00:13:03,960
but he passed away years ago.

265
00:13:04,080 --> 00:13:05,410
She has no other family.

266
00:13:06,040 --> 00:13:07,100
Then it's a friend.

267
00:13:07,800 --> 00:13:09,240
A very close one.

268
00:13:13,960 --> 00:13:16,620
Why isn't there a single photo of them together?

269
00:13:19,440 --> 00:13:20,400
I'm getting old.

270
00:13:20,400 --> 00:13:21,730
My memory's failing me.

271
00:13:29,880 --> 00:13:31,080
Come to think of it,

272
00:13:32,240 --> 00:13:34,770
there is only this one photo of them together.

273
00:13:35,040 --> 00:13:37,040
It makes them look really shabby.

274
00:13:37,280 --> 00:13:40,720
"Former opera actress Jin Guizhi becomes a prostitute."

275
00:13:40,800 --> 00:13:43,640
"Famous star Yun Feiyan claims son on the street."

276
00:13:43,640 --> 00:13:45,200
Isn't Boss Yun a woman?

277
00:13:46,720 --> 00:13:49,920
What is the relationship between Jin Guizhi and Boss Yun?

278
00:13:50,520 --> 00:13:52,000
Jin Guizhi

279
00:13:52,640 --> 00:13:54,300
was Boss Yun's junior sister.

280
00:13:54,760 --> 00:13:56,760
They were in the same troupe.

281
00:13:56,800 --> 00:13:57,660
Junior sister?

282
00:13:58,200 --> 00:14:00,060
How did she end up as a prostitute?

283
00:14:00,080 --> 00:14:02,280
That reporter made it up.

